gov.nasa.worldwind.symbology
Interface TacticalQuad

All Superinterfaces:
AVList, Highlightable, Movable, Renderable, TacticalGraphic
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractRectangularGraphic, RectangularFireSupportArea, RectangularPositionArea, RectangularTarget
public interface TacticalQuad
extends TacticalGraphic

An interface for tactical graphics shaped like a quadrilaterals. This interface provides methods to set the length and width of the quad. The length and width can also be set using the SymbologyConstants.DISTANCE modifier.

See Also:
TacticalGraphicFactory.createQuad(String, Iterable, gov.nasa.worldwind.avlist.AVList)
